| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6955 — Recovery Inhibition (blacknevas)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7d5a4833-a22d-5761-8a38-b7cd9954cb63"
